# BazaarChecklist

## Before large changes

- Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md), [docs/PRODUCT.md](docs/PRODUCT.md), and [docs/DATA_MODEL.md](docs/DATA_MODEL.md).
- Do not assume MVP features that are still marked pending or TBD in PRODUCT.

## Stack

- Flutter app in `mobile/`; Firebase (Auth, Firestore) for v1; no Ruby/server unless docs say so.

## Safety

- Never commit API keys, `google-services.json`, `GoogleService-Info.plist`, or private keys.
- Align mobile and web; avoid platform forks unless documented.

## Edits

- Match existing style; avoid unrelated refactors.
- Update docs when changing product scope or data shapes.

---

**Rule scope**: This rule uses `alwaysApply: true`. If you prefer it only for Dart/Flutter files, change frontmatter to `alwaysApply: false` and set `globs` e.g. `mobile/**/*.dart`.
